{"tid":1882614,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日檔案[粵/普]       ","createTime":"2020-02-16T11:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T11:25:01.000Z","uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a5361b9d8fbd436122c79e9995bd784ec52a0cf","tid":1882614,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:04:19.000Z","msg":"星期日檔案[粵/普]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎的危機席捲全球，口罩作為個人防護裝備的第一道防線，頓成瘋搶的主角。香港的口罩供應已數度斷貨，近日更愈見升溫，市民為撲口罩各施各法，就連代理商和藥房也為找貨源苦惱。有居港的外國商人由家鄉運入大量口罩，免費供應給資訊較缺乏的人士和低收入家庭，以解燃眉之急，也有區議員為街坊團購口罩，並申請區議會撥款製作「防炎包」。一個口罩，一個保障，可以到哪裡找？又怎樣反映香港情？"},{"pid":"3ad39977ab9bc42f06580d4ac7f87f7730dd8978","tid":1882614,"uid":215228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"唉香港食得屎<br />\n<br />\n幾打幾打咁食"},{"pid":"305a0abed58f16fe02d74442413aaeeaa713c35c","tid":1882614,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"帶到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345955fd094543422fef839f814675f006d7f2f3","tid":1882614,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"問下自己投邊個"},{"pid":"620f88555b1256954f6a1f7cd68a893191bc284b","tid":1882614,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cb317558a8764d22521303f0bec54848a44f1f","tid":1882614,"uid":276415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"盾牌？"},{"pid":"013de6c78c5b3e130bbf8668cda5bf2f15d02882","tid":1882614,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9cb317558a8764d22521303f0bec54848a44f1f","tid":1882614,"uid":276415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"盾牌？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"今日比人屌到開花<img src=\"/